                            <comment id="14190250" author="metatech" created="Thu, 30 Oct 2014 15:42:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch &quot;fi.patch&quot; does the filtering on the full path, and not only the file name.  This is not aligned with the &quot;FilenameFilter&quot; defined in the constructor of the DirectoryWatcher class.&lt;br/&gt;
